+++ b/orderflow_services/runbook_ml_phase2_12_v1.md
@@ -0,0 +1,49 @@
+# Phase 2.12 — Routing Incident RCA Provider/Prompt Routing Controller
+
+## Цель
+Использовать decisions из `routing incident RCA usefulness governor` для выбора:
+- `provider`
+- `model_name`
+- `prompt_version`
+- `policy_version`
+
+Сначала только в `DRY_RUN`.
+
+## Входы
+- `stream:ml:operator_rca_routing_rca_requests`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor_decisions`
+- Redis policy hashes `cfg:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor:*`
+
+## Выходы
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_decisions`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_audit`
+- `stream:ml:operator_rca_routing_rca_requests_routed`
+- `metrics:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing:last`
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_governor_decisions + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_decisions + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_audit + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_rca_routing_rca_requests_routed + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli HGETALL metrics:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing:last
+curl -s localhost:9890/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_'
+```
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_ROUTING_MODE=DRY_RUN
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_DEFAULT_PROVIDER=vertex
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_DEFAULT_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash-lite
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_DEFAULT_PROMPT_VERSION=routing_incident_rca_v1
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_DEFAULT_POLICY_VERSION=policy_v1
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- suppress/promote применяется только к routing-incident RCA routing
+- commit в default route допускается только если `ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_RCA_ROUTING_MODE=COMMIT`
